description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 36, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 36, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 1 for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30361-21181-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [36 Votes, Common]
